{"segment_id": "shijing__song-chengong-007__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-chengong-007", "source_id": "song-chengong-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·臣工之什·007.1", "text_original": "有來雝雝，至止肅肅。相維辟公，天子穆穆。於薦廣牡，相予肆祀。", "text_normalized": "有來雝雝，至止肅肅。相維辟公，天子穆穆。於薦廣牡，相予肆祀。", "notes": "雝 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-chengong-007__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-chengong-007", "source_id": "song-chengong-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·臣工之什·007.2", "text_original": "假哉皇考，綏予孝子。宣哲維人，文武維后。燕及皇天，克昌厥後。", "text_normalized": "假哉皇考，綏予孝子。宣哲維人，文武維后。燕及皇天，克昌厥後。", "notes": "雝 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-chengong-007__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-chengong-007", "source_id": "song-chengong-007__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·臣工之什·007.3", "text_original": "綏我眉壽，介以繁祉。既右烈考，亦右文母。", "text_normalized": "綏我眉壽，介以繁祉。既右烈考，亦右文母。", "notes": "雝 Chinese stanza 3."}
